In technology, you don’t want to mindlessly chase trends — but you also don’t want them to leave you behind. In that spirit, about a year ago we decided to look into all of this AI business and see what it had to do with Tailscale. Our CEO and co-founder Avery Pennarun describes what we found in a new piece called (spoiler alert!) “AI companies are surprisingly normal.” (https://info.tailscale.com/e3t/Ctc/OT+113/d4K34c04/VX6PKt3ThBqKN53JZwHKpKNyW22vCbp5njjX9N7swVvT3l5QzW69sMD-6lZ3q7W2C2rBH27HRnLW77fSyh20Zr8fW1dJRkM5kFLmCW7QjnxJ7xKzH9W7bj_2D1FbXH4W19SVg_3HVrxhW6DXC_d5W-rNGW5tJFcp8JJCc5W8D9f8-6c6Qd6W9gFdQ67Nvs5ZW8598KR6zCMjtN7TZtmhjJgsTW5y4B0M1tVhFqN1qKpscsjGXjW7HgrLt1B-J9hW8Nj3mw5JwBd0W2WtC7d19_KdMN9lSPCmPtR8yVpRHS94xvVNsW3hMJ2L78tN_Rf7KGnJv04 )

